00:11:14.800 --> 00:11:15.760
Dokter Veer!

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:34.040
Kejar mereka!

00:11:42.680 --> 00:11:44.120
Ayolah, tuan tanah.

00:11:45.080 --> 00:11:46.960
Aku akan membawamu ke penjara.

